{"body":"\"<div class=\\\"govspeak\\\"><h2 id=\\\"type-of-application\\\">Type of application:</h2>\\n\\n<p>Full Planning Application</p>\\n\\n<h2 id=\\\"applicant-name\\\">Applicant name:</h2>\\n\\n<p>Fairhold Brislington Ltd</p>\\n\\n<h2 id=\\\"site-address\\\">Site address:</h2>\\n\\n<p>1 Repton Road, Brislington, Bristol, BS4 3LS</p>\\n\\n<h2 id=\\\"description-of-proposed-development\\\">Description of proposed development:</h2>\\n\\n<p>External Alteration to existing building</p>\\n\\n<h2 id=\\\"case-officer\\\">Case Officer:</h2>\\n\\n<p>Section 62A Applications Team</p>\\n\\n<h2 id=\\\"procedure\\\">Procedure:</h2>\\n\\n<p>Written Representations</p>\\n\\n<h2 id=\\\"key-dates\\\">Key dates:</h2>\\n\\n<table>\\n  <thead>\\n    <tr>\\n      <td></td>\\n      <th scope=\\\"col\\\">Date</th>\\n    </tr>\\n  </thead>\\n  <tbody>\\n    <tr>\\n      <th scope=\\\"row\\\">Date application valid</th>\\n      <td>26 July 2024</td>\\n    </tr>\\n    <tr>\\n      <th scope=\\\"row\\\">Date by when representations must be made</th>\\n      <td>2 September 2024</td>\\n    </tr>\\n    <tr>\\n      <th scope=\\\"row\\\">Hearing date and venue</th>\\n      <td>N/A</td>\\n    </tr>\\n    <tr>\\n      <th scope=\\\"row\\\">Target Decision</th>\\n      <td>20 September 2024</td>\\n    </tr>\\n    <tr>\\n      <th scope=\\\"row\\\">Decision date</th>\\n      <td>18 September 2024</td>\\n    </tr>\\n  </tbody>\\n</table>\\n\\n<h2 id=\\\"decision\\\">Decision</h2>\\n<ul>\\n  <li><span class=\\\"gem-c-attachment-link\\\">\\n  <a class=\\\"govuk-link\\\" href=\\\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/66eaef429975b7a980b3053c/S62A_2024_0056_Decision_Notice_and_Statement_of_reasons.pdf\\\">Decision Notice and Statement of reasons</a>  (<span class=\\\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\\\"><abbr title=\\\"Portable Document Format\\\" class=\\\"gem-c-attachment-link__abbr\\\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\\\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\\\">143 KB</span>, <span class=\\\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\\\">9 pages</span>)</span></li>\\n</ul>\\n\\n<h2 id=\\\"make-a-representation\\\">Make a representation</h2>\\n\\n<p>The application can be inspected under the application plans and documents heading below.</p>\\n\\n<p>You will be able to comment on this application until 2 September 2024</p>\\n\\n<div class=\\\"call-to-action\\\">\\n  <p>Please base your comments on planning matters.</p>\\n\\n  <p>Please avoid the use of inflammatory, discriminatory or abusive comments.</p>\\n\\n  <p>All representations made in connection with the development proposal will be made publicly available on the website shortly after the end of the representation period.  The name of the individual author or organisation will be published however addresses, signatures and contact details will not be published.  We advise you not to include any other personal information about yourself or others. <br>\\nOur <a href=\\\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/planning-inspectorate-privacy-notices/customer-privacy-notice\\\" class=\\\"govuk-link\\\">Customer Privacy Notice</a> sets out how we handle personal data in accordance with the law.</p>\\n\\n  <p>Send your comments via email to <a href=\\\"mailto:section62anonmajor@planninginspectorate.gov.uk\\\" class=\\\"govuk-link\\\">section62anonmajor@planninginspectorate.gov.uk</a></p>\\n\\n  <p>or write to</p>\\n  <div class=\\\"address\\\"><div class=\\\"adr org fn\\\"><p>\\nSection 62A Applications Team<br>The Planning Inspectorate<br>3rd Floor<br>Temple Quay House<br>2 The Square<br>Temple Quay<br>Bristol<br>BS1 6PN\\n</p></div></div>\\n\\n  <p><strong>Sending comments by email will enable us to deal with them more quickly and is preferred.</strong></p>\\n\\n  <p>Please include the application reference number S62A/2024/0056 and site address.</p>\\n\\n  <p>This application will be determined by an Inspector appointed by the Secretary of State. Shortly after the close of the representation period the Planning Inspectorate will consider whether a hearing is necessary. In the event that a hearing is scheduled, and you would wish to speak at the hearing, you must make this request at the time you submit your written representations.</p>\\n\\n  <p>Where the application is to be considered at a hearing, notice of the date, time and venue for the hearing along with the name of the person holding the hearing, will be published on this website at least one week before the date of the hearing.</p>\\n</div>\\n\\n<h2 id=\\\"application-plans-and-documents\\\">Application Plans and Documents</h2>\\n\\n<ul>\\n  <li><span class=\\\"gem-c-attachment-link\\\">\\n  <a class=\\\"govuk-link\\\" href=\\\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/66aa15bffc8e12ac3edb083c/3M-455__-_Cover_Letter_-_External_Alterations_Redacted.pdf\\\">3M-455 - Cover Letter - External Alterations</a>  (<span class=\\\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\\\"><abbr title=\\\"Portable Document Format\\\" class=\\\"gem-c-attachment-link__abbr\\\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\\\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\\\">111 KB</span>, <span class=\\\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\\\">2 pages</span>)</span></li>\\n  <li><span class=\\\"gem-c-attachment-link\\\">\\n  <a class=\\\"govuk-link\\\" href=\\\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/66acce95a3c2a28abb50dc41/Application_form_Redacted0056.pdf\\\">Application form</a>  (<span class=\\\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\\\"><abbr title=\\\"Portable Document Format\\\" class=\\\"gem-c-attachment-link__abbr\\\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\\\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\\\">4.65 MB</span>, <span class=\\\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\\\">14 pages</span>)</span></li>\\n  <li><span class=\\\"gem-c-attachment-link\\\">\\n  <a class=\\\"govuk-link\\\" href=\\\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/66aa15bfa3c2a28abb50daaf/PL01_Rev___Existing_Location_Plan_and_Site_Plan_Redacted.pdf\\\">PL01 Rev Existing Location  Plan and Site Plan</a>  (<span class=\\\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\\\"><abbr title=\\\"Portable Document Format\\\" class=\\\"gem-c-attachment-link__abbr\\\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\\\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\\\">57 KB</span>, <span class=\\\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\\\">1 page</span>)</span></li>\\n  <li><span class=\\\"gem-c-attachment-link\\\">\\n  <a class=\\\"govuk-link\\\" href=\\\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/66aa15bfa3c2a28abb50dab0/PL02_Rev___Existing_and_Proposed_Floor_Plans_Redacted.pdf\\\">PL02 Rev Existing and Proposed Floor Plans</a>  (<span class=\\\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\\\"><abbr title=\\\"Portable Document Format\\\" class=\\\"gem-c-attachment-link__abbr\\\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\\\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\\\">47.3 KB</span>, <span class=\\\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\\\">1 page</span>)</span></li>\\n  <li><span class=\\\"gem-c-attachment-link\\\">\\n  <a class=\\\"govuk-link\\\" href=\\\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/66aa15bf0808eaf43b50dad7/PL03_Rev___Existing_Elevations_Redacted.pdf\\\">PL03 Rev Existing_Elevations</a>  (<span class=\\\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\\\"><abbr title=\\\"Portable Document Format\\\" class=\\\"gem-c-attachment-link__abbr\\\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\\\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\\\">370 KB</span>, <span class=\\\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\\\">1 page</span>)</span></li>\\n  <li><span class=\\\"gem-c-attachment-link\\\">\\n  <a class=\\\"govuk-link\\\" href=\\\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/66aa15bf0808eaf43b50dad9/PL04_Rev___Proposed_Site_Plan_Redacted.pdf\\\">PL04 Rev Proposed Site Plan</a>  (<span class=\\\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\\\"><abbr title=\\\"Portable Document Format\\\" class=\\\"gem-c-attachment-link__abbr\\\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\\\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\\\">42.7 KB</span>, <span class=\\\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\\\">1 page</span>)</span></li>\